<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Hochgeborn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, unser willig
                            <expan>und<ex>er</ex>tenig</expan> dienst sein
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit fleiss voran bereyt. Und als uns ewr
                        gnade <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ir von
                                <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>merklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künig, meynt <expan>zu reite<ex>n</ex></expan>, und begert
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> des ein urlawb <expan>zu
                            bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr gnade <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir das an
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde des rats bracht und also zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, daz sie
                        das iren <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen sein; doch also ob sie
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> in der zeit, die ir also awszen wurdt sein,
                                <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tun <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir denn <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>et</expan> und tut, als ir in pflichtig
                        seyt, und auch <expan>desgleiche<ex>n</ex></expan> mit den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> zu tun bestellt. Denn von der
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt etc.,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> Casparn <expan>Lyenberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>müntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. <lb/>Peter <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>se<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">or</hi></expan> und Wilhelm Mendel zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
